Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, adduser, curl
Recommends: logrotate
Description: Acme.sh is a single file LetsEncrypt shell script client.
 Acme.sh is a single file LetsEncrypt shell script client. Usually it is
 installed and run in a users home directory. This debian package installs
 acme.sh as system binary. The configuration is adopted to the debian way.
 It is not intended to use manually but to run by a cron job.
